Title: Veggie Packed BBQ Meatloaf
Instruction: Preheat oven to 200°C/180°C fan-forced. Lightly spray a 10cm x 18cm loaf tin with oil and line 2 long sides with baking paper, extending paper 2cm above edges of pan
